MENU_PKG_VNC
  Here you will find options for VNC.

SDECFG_PKG_VNC_X_SERVER
  This option enables the build of the stand-alone X server. The build
  takes rather long since it builds a whole X server and might be disabled
  when just the viewer is needed.
